---
---

<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container hero-content">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Python · AI/ML Инженер</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Богдан<br />Атрошенко</h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">
      Проектирую RAG-системы и мультиагентные пайплайны.<br class="br-desktop" />
      Превращаю сложные задачи в работающие решения.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a class="btn btn--primary" href="#projects">Проекты</a>
      <a class="btn btn--outline" href="#contacts">Написать мне</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a class="scroll-hint" href="#about" aria-label="Листать вниз">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"></path>
    </svg>
  </a>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* gradient background mesh */
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 70% 30%, var(--accent-glow), transparent),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 20% 80%, rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.06), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding-top: 100px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    animation: fade-up 0.7s ease 0.1s both;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 9vw, 7.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    animation: fade-up 0.8s ease 0.2s both;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.6vw, 1.2rem);
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-bottom: 44px;
    animation: fade-up 0.8s ease 0.35s both;
  }

  .br-desktop { display: none; }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    animation: fade-up 0.8s ease 0.5s both;
  }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 2;
    color: var(--muted);
    opacity: 0.6;
    animation: fade-in 1s ease 1.2s both, bob 2.4s ease-in-out 1.5s infinite;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .scroll-hint:hover { opacity: 1; }

  @keyframes bob {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px); }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .br-desktop { display: block; }
  }
</style>
